casebody.data:
No. 108,

Orig.

Nebraska v. Wyoming et al.

Third motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded $97,843.24 to be paid to him 20 percent by the United States and 40 percent each by the States of Nebraska and Wyoming. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 492 U. S. 903.]
